{"tid":1360603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈反對十八鄉鄉事委員會干預市民遊行自由","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:46:05.000Z","uid":283781,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba65400e442c502dac736316b3bcee6a2984d8aa","tid":1360603,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n   <br />\n<ins><strong>強烈反對十八鄉鄉事委員會干預市民遊行自由</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n本討論區就十八鄉鄉事委員會於今日去信警務處一事表示強烈反對。該會於信中表示網上流傳將攻擊南邊圍一事屬嚴重指控，卻沒有任何根據，無中生有。該會於信中亦提到一切後果將全部由警方負責，其言論氣燄囂張，有涉恐嚇警方之嫌。本討論區要求該會撤回所有失實指控並就事件向有關人士道歉。<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n                                              <div style=\"text-align: right;\">眾連登網友</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月24日"},{"pid":"bff0f961af2e511787482018d1a7f238b1cf60eb","tid":1360603,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"小弟中文不才 歡迎指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc66a1007bb5df0c78643736357c412094260771","tid":1360603,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbead281b548a2d5b856aefd0884a85ce241d865","tid":1360603,"uid":283781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dd9b77d7c896706f4b6f8c30dd9a9cb3896a7f","tid":1360603,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:35:46.000Z","msg":"而家係咪入元朗權利都無，商店損失係咪佢地負責"},{"pid":"e74ee01fca87818bbea3b5e05ad23e9d1bfe6c9c","tid":1